### ========================================
### Profile Management
### ========================================

### Get My Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update My Profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "displayName": "John Updated",
  "username": "johnupdated",
  "bio": "Software developer and tech enthusiast",
  "statusMessage": "Available for chat"
}

### Change Password
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/me/change-password
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "currentPassword": "SecurePass123!",
  "newPassword": "NewSecurePass456!"
}

### ========================================
### Avatar Upload
### ========================================

### Request Avatar Upload URL
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/me/avatar/request-upload
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "fileName": "avatar.jpg",
  "mimeType": "image/jpeg",
  "fileSize": 524288
}

### Confirm Avatar Upload
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/me/avatar/confirm-upload
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "fileKey": "avatars/462d51ff-8e29-48a5-99b9-a23ee6813332/94ee214453c16a21b1389e5d21611872.jpg"
}

### ========================================
### User Search
### ========================================

### Search Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/search?query=ebu&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========================================
### Email Verification
### ========================================

### Verify Email (Public)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/verify-email
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "token": "ab0e242d20fbbced51e881a1eb22d167da50eeb76da3b7eb4a33cecf1853dc9e"
}

### Resend Verification Email (Public)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/resend-verification
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com"
}

### Send Verification Email (Authenticated)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/me/send-verification
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

